headline: Green Stocks Are Big Winners as Tech Boom Drives Energy Demand
summary: Instead, the sector is booming as artificial intelligence powers massive demand for all kinds of energy.  The S&P Global Clean Energy Transition Index has rallied  this year, handily beating a  advance in the S&P 500 Index.  It’s also outpacing an  gain in the S&P Global Oil Index, which was expected to be a big winner on the back of Trump’s “drill, baby, drill” agenda.
